This is Perl module Method::Destructor.

INSTALLATION

Method::Destructor installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    $ cpan Method::Destructor

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

Method::Destructor documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc Method::Destructor

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

